  "content": "\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan class=\"h-card\" translate=\"no\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://infosec.exchange/@sudorandom\" class=\"u-url mention\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e@\u003cspan\u003esudorandom\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e nice story!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIt's like the tale of a maintenance person who is brought on a ship to fix the engine. He enters the engine room, looks at it, and then hits it a few times with a hammer. Suddenly, the engine starts running.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhen presenting with a bill of a thousand dollars, the shipowner is flabbergasted. But the maintenance person can explain his price convincingly:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e- $5: five hits with a hammer\u003cbr\u003e- $995: knowing where to hit\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e The fix might be small, but knowing where to implement the fix is where the real magic happens.\u003c/p\u003e",
